data.title: Easton Family YMCA @ Peachblossom
data.text:
The rockwall is an exhilarating activity you can enjoy at the Easton YMCA! Climbing is a fantastic full body workout that is fun for everybody! Our experienced instructors will walk you through harnessing, tying in and will give you personal instruction for your first climb. We invite anybody ages 5-105 to climb!

Every “Y” is Your “Y” in the YMCA of the Chesapeake. Your membership gives you access to all 11 Eastern Shore area branches, as well as every YMCA in Maryland, and most branches Nationwide!

We have programs for all ages! Offering fitness classes, swim lessons, afterschool care, sports, and camp, the YMCA helps build healthy families. Explore the Y and click here to see what seasonal programs are available for registration.

Are you interested in coaching? Want to help with youth programs for a volunteer opportunity your whole family can participate in? When we all join, we rise together! Please contact the Y at 410-822-0566.

Every year, we rely on donations to help ensure that all of the people in our community can access our services. There are lots of ways you can give, and we’re grateful for your help. Together we can make a difference.

All branches of the YMCA of the Chesapeake will be closed all day on the following holidays: New Year's Day, Good Friday, Easter Sunday, Memorial Day, Fourth of July, Labor Day, Thanksgiving Day, Christmas Day.
